          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Originating as a small, family-run ecommerce furniture business, we embarked on a mission to pioneer seamless and convenient online furniture services nationwide. After years of hard work and dedication, our dreams came true on Honeypot Lane in Grantham, where Honeypot Furniture was born. Since then, we have continually grown and evolved, offering quality furnishings and a premium shopping experience to homes across the nation.<\/p>",
